headline.print_headline: All Blacks Retain Bledisloe Cup With Crushing Win
headline.main: All Blacks Retain Bledisloe Cup With Crushing Win

lead_paragraph: New Zealand's forwards responded to criticism of their performance in their opening Rugby Championship clash to set the foundation for a 51-20 victory over Australia at Eden Park on Saturday that also ensured the retention of the Bledisloe Cup.
